abstract: An interesting ceremony took place lately at the Church at Versailles, where Madame Goujon celebrated by a mass the 100th anniversary of her birthday. abstract: On the evening of the 14th inst., a force of 7,500 federalists, under General BLANCO, suddenly and unexpectedly made their appearance in Taczoaya, a village in this valley, five miles distant from this capital. But when the last became known, the wildest confusion prevailed.
